messages.message: Shared accounts can have 2FA as long as 2FA is configured using 1password Authenticator.
Hey folks, here's the demo video: https://drive.google.com/file/d/19LzerPW6s0ifgRS_IDYxULjtS472Y7CI/view?usp=drive_link
It shows how to add credits to an AI Hub license!

If I'm understanding right, you'll only be able to adjust credits for your own account, and only if you're an admin. Are we considering making the entire SE team admins?

If not, is there a way for an admin to add credits for another non-admin user?
